The paper discusses a practical solution to the problem of optimizing software for various hardware configurations, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of autotuning infrastructure and repository of knowledge suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence and machine learning, which are relevant to the categories of cs.AR (Artificial Intelligence), cs.PL (Programming Languages), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions the optimization of resource usage, which is related to the category of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
